    TrackSOM-workflow

    ExportClusteringDetailsOnly

    ExportClusteringDetailsOnly.Rd

    Given a TrackSOM object export the clustering result as data.table.

    Usage

    ExportClusteringDetailsOnly(tracksom.result)

    Arguments

    tracksom.result

    TrackSOM object as generated by TrackSOM

    Value

    Data.table containing the meta cluster, cluster, and tracking ids for all the cells

    Examples

    data_files <- sapply(c(0:4), function(i) {
system.file("extdata", paste0("synthetic_d", i, ".fcs"), package="TrackSOM")
})
use_cols <- c("x", "y", "z")
tracksom_result <- TrackSOM(inputFiles = data_files,
                            colsToUse = use_cols,
                            nClus = 10,
                            dataFileType = ".fcs"
)
